Copyright 2026 Sim Yunsup

This product includes software derived from Open Code Review
(alibaba/open-code-review), licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
(https://github.com/alibaba/open-code-review).

Derived material:
  - The review rule taxonomy (security-focused rule set + severity levels).
  - The deterministic review pipeline design:
    diff parsing -> file bundling -> rule matching -> review packet.

Changes from the original:
  - Reimplemented in TypeScript (the original is written in Go).
  - Removed the model-calling agent entirely. sereview never calls any LLM
    and requires no API key; the host Claude Code session performs the
    review instead.
